Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:16.98,Lyrics EN,,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:26.12,Lyrics EN,,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 017—\NVictory is not everything{NOTE:勝利と敗北の間}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.67,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:54.12,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,You wagered the construction of the new gym on winning with the Soviet Union?{NOTE:バレー部XXX体育館建設をソ連との試合にかかってるんですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:58.04,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,So if we don't win with the Soviet Union, there's no gym?{NOTE:と言うことは、ソ連に勝たなければ、体育館をXXXてことね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:58.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.{NOTE:え。そうなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:03.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,This is why we have to win with the Soviet Union no matter what.{NOTE:だからこうなったらあたしたち何が何でもソ連に勝たなければ成らないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.94,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.06,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,No matter what?{NOTE:何が何でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Precisely.{NOTE:そうよ。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Let's win.{NOTE:勝ちましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why are you so quiet all of the sudden?{NOTE:皆、どうしたの？黙ってしまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:16.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Where's the usual "Yeah! Let's do this!"?{NOTE:「よし、やろう」って言ってくれないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:21.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yeah. You all were so enthusiastic in front of professor Hongou earlier.{NOTE:そうよ。本郷先生からソ連との試合聞いた時、皆あんなに張り切ってなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Or do you want to say you lost your confidence?{NOTE:それとも、それとも皆ソ連に勝つ自身をなくしてしまったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Hey, Kakko.{NOTE:ね、カッコ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What about you?{NOTE:あなたはどうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.52,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Well, I am confident all right.{NOTE:そ、それはあたしだって自身があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.42,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But what?{NOTE:でもなんなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.93,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,But saying that we have to win no matter the costs is a little too much.{NOTE:ん、でもさ、「何が何でも絶対に勝つ」なんて、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:46.35,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,But I doubt prof. Hongou left us as a part of his strategy like Hayakawa-san said he did.{NOTE:だって、本郷先生はコーチ降りたのは早川さんが言うように本当に作戦上のことかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.92,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, do you really believe it?{NOTE:ね、早川さん、あなたはそう言い切れる自身があって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.14,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,You don't, right?{NOTE:ないよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.33,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,No way. Nope.{NOTE:ない、ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Our opponent is the Soviet Union that even our high schools can't win with.{NOTE:XXX相手は日本の高校チームが構わない、ソ連チームだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:02.54,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,No matter how confident we are, we're a\hlittle worried without professor Hongou.{NOTE:そうよ。いくら自身があっても、毎日本郷先生のコーチがなって、やっぱり少し不安な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.02,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.70,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,That All-Japan tournament was a good example.{NOTE:今度の全国大会の優勝がいい見本よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.62,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,We stand no chance without professor Hongou.{NOTE:本郷先生はいなきゃ、やっぱりむりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.18,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,We can't say for sure that we will win by ourselves.{NOTE:あたしたちだけじゃ絶対勝てるて言い切らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.85,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,No matter our confidence. Right?{NOTE:いくら自身があっても。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:13.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,This is bad.{NOTE:行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.40,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I feared it would come to this.{NOTE:恐れていた時代成ってしまったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Girls, aren't you forgetting something?{NOTE:皆、何か勘違いしてるんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy's volleyball club is the best in Japan.{NOTE:富士見学園バレー部は日本一なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,So what if they're the Soviet Union?{NOTE:ソ連が何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:32.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If our seniors can win with them, why can't we do the same?{NOTE:あたしたちの先輩はソ連に勝てるように、あたしたちだって勝てないわけがないじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,As long as I believe in myself, I won't lose.{NOTE:その自身があるかぎり、あたしは絶対に負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:38.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Or better put, I will win.{NOTE:いえ、勝てると言う確信があるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.28,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yep. I think we can win too.{NOTE:あたしも勝てると思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.41,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Really?\N– Yep.{NOTE:—そう？\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I watched the last Soviet Union's game on the TV.{NOTE:この間もテレビのソ連の試合振りを見て思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Because of it, I am sure we can win.{NOTE:あたしたちは勝てるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:50.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No. There's no way Fujimi Academy can do anything but win with the Soviet Union.{NOTE:いいえ。ソ連を倒すのはわが富士見学園バレー部以外にはないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Let's do this, girls.{NOTE:やりましょう、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.57,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Yep. – All right.\N– Let's do this.{NOTE:—うん。—うん。\\N—やろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.89,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Yeah, yeah.\N– All right.{NOTE:—やろうやろう。ね？\\N—やるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.43,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Let's do our best.\N– Right.{NOTE:—XXX。—皆、頑張れね。—そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Let's practice the spike. Assume positions.{NOTE:さ、千本スパイクよ。位置について。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.56,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Okay!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.01,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Here I go.\N– OK.{NOTE:—行くわよ。\\N—OK。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.36,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,All right!{NOTE:XXX。それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.23,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.63,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on.\NWhatcha doing?{NOTE:ほらほらほら、何やってんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.52,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.29,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.79,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Here I go!{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Don't lose your focus!{NOTE:XXX、いいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:40.99,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.22,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.41,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:44.82,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.28,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Pass!{NOTE:パス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.45,Default,Ozawa,0,0,0,,Don't be such a klutz.{NOTE:だらしないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.80,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,I won't lose.{NOTE:負けるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Naka, we won't win with the Soviets like this.{NOTE:ナカ、そんなことじゃソ連に勝てないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We won't win with the Soviets like this…?{NOTE:そんなことじゃソ連に勝てない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What if?{NOTE:もし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, it can't be.{NOTE:いえ、そんなことは絶対にないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.24,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But what if we lost by any chance?{NOTE:でも、万が一ソ連にまけたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:いいえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.16,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, but…{NOTE:いいえ、でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.92,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You lost to the Soviet Union after all?{NOTE:やっぱりソ連に負けたじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.63,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You're hopeless.{NOTE:だめだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:19.04,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,– I thought you were confident you'll win?\N{こうなったX新体育館もうじゃね。}– It's a goodbye to the new gym then.{NOTE:勝つ自身があると言ったのは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.74,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You won a single championship and you got this conceited already.{NOTE:中々XXX優勝XXXこうなるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.78,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You don't know your place.{NOTE:これで無量ほどしたでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.58,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You should just disband the club!{NOTE:このさえバレー部なんか解散しろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:31.00,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,Disband! Disband!{NOTE:XXX！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.00,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stop it.{NOTE:止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Anything but disbanding it.{NOTE:解散だけは許して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:35.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Please.{NOTE:お願いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.58,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,Disband.{NOTE:解散。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:39.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stop!{NOTE:止めて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.56,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,Disband.{NOTE:解散。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:45.44,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,Disband!{NOTE:解散。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.64,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stop!{NOTE:止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.32,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:54.32,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,– Are you feeling unwell?\N– It's nothing.{NOTE:—ね、気分は悪いの？\\N—なんでもないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. Let's get at it.{NOTE:さ、皆、張り切ってきましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:05:59.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can win with the Soviets?{NOTE:あなたは本当にソ連に勝てる自身があるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If I lost, I couldn't face the others.{NOTE:負ければ皆の前で宣言なんてしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll win.{NOTE:勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We will show you a victory with the Soviets.{NOTE:ソ連との試合を勝って見せます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:36.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I was sure of this back then when I said those words.{NOTE:言ってしまった後、あたしはXXXしまったと思った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even though I believe in us, one can't know the outcome until after the match.{NOTE:勝つ自身があっても、試合はやってみなければ分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.28,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I went ahead and said that already.{NOTE:でも、もう言ってしまったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:44.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I've declared our win in front of everyone.{NOTE:もう皆の前ではっきり宣言してしまったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's no going back.{NOTE:賽は投げられたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:53.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Besides, the club members still believe my words.{NOTE:それに、あたしの「絶対に勝とう」って言う言葉を信じてくれるメンバー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,At this point there's no option but to win.{NOTE:ここまで来たら、何が何でも絶対勝つ以外はないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll win for sure.{NOTE:いえ。きっと勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:06.80,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll triumph over Tsutomu-san and people who've underestimated our club.{NOTE:そして努さんXXX、バレーをXXX人たち、皆を見返してやるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:12.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But professor Hongou's resignation just before this important game was unfair.{NOTE:でもそのためにも本郷先生が一番大事な試合の時にコーチおりるなんて卑怯だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:17.24,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's no way I could answer on the spot as to why I'm playing volleyball.{NOTE:「何のためにバレーをやるか」なんて聞かれてもすぐ答えられるわけがないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:21.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The match that is right in front of our eyes is much more important than that.{NOTE:そんなことより目の前にXXX試合に勝つことのほうが大事なのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And yet.{NOTE:なのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.57,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And yet…{NOTE:なのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If it only was one of his usual strategic tricks.{NOTE:これが先生の例の作戦だったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.28,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If only that was the case.{NOTE:そうでありますように。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.00,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, it's no good.{NOTE:いいえ、行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I must stay strong.{NOTE:XXXあたしはそんなに弱気入った行けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,A willpower to win is crucial.{NOTE:大事のは勝ってる自身。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.38,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,With or without professor Hongou.{NOTE:例え本郷先生がいなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:52.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We will win.{NOTE:勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We will win!{NOTE:勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Japan Times{NOTE:日日タイムス}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:07:59.93,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:00.68,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.42,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Don't fall asleep.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.76,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,– Keep it together!\N– Yeah, yeah, yeah.{NOTE:—しっかりしてよ！\\N—XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.46,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,The match with the Soviet Union takes place in two days. Do you feel confident?{NOTE:いよいよソ連との試合が明後日に迫っただけど、どう？自身がある？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.84,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean by that?{NOTE:え？そう言うことはどう言うことな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.78,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Surely you don't mean you will win?{NOTE:まさか勝てると言う自身があるわけじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Precisely, I do.{NOTE:え。そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am confident we will win.{NOTE:勝てると言う自身のことです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:21.08,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,I'd like to remind you that even the Japanese high schools are no match for your opponents.{NOTE:いくらなんだって君、相手は日本の高校生XXX腕XXXなんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:26.00,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Even though Fujimi Academy's the best in Japan, they're the best in the world.{NOTE:富士見学園は日本一と言っても、ジュニア中が世界一なんだからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.93,Default,Reporter C,0,0,0,,Of course, you're aware of that already, aren't you?{NOTE:もちろんそれを承知Xで言ってるんでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That is correct.{NOTE:もちろんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.94,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,You don't say.{NOTE:まさか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll show you a victory.{NOTE:絶対に勝って見せます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:44.36,Sign,,0,0,0,,The anticipated Japan-Soviet match is tomorrow!{NOTE:いよいよ明日に迫る日ソ親善ジュニアバレーボール…}
Comment: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.85,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,After wagering their honor, will they win against the Soviet Union?{NOTE:日本一の面目にかけてソ連チームに一矢を報いるか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.81,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Check this out.{NOTE:見てみろよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.81,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Wow, so cool.{NOTE:ワ、かっこいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.38,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,But can they really win?{NOTE:でも本当に勝てるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.34,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Of course they can.{NOTE:当たり前さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.48,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Our school's heroine Kozue-san declared it so, so it will be this way.{NOTE:わが効のXXXこずえはとうとう宣言しただもん。勝つに決まってるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.99,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to this game.{NOTE:明日の試合が楽しみね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.99,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,We'd better reserve good seats.{NOTE:XXXいい席を取ろうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Please get one for me too.{NOTE:あたしのも頼む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.48,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,I'll cheer her on with all might.{NOTE:(XXX・かすれる)まで応援するわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.68,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,She'll lead our school straight to a victory.{NOTE:ソ連チームにXXストレート勝ちだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.94,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Wah, she's here, she's here.{NOTE:ワ。来た来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.64,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ayuhara-san!\N– Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:—鮎原さん。\\N鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.78,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Do your best!\N– Good luck!{NOTE:—おい、頑張れよ！\\N—頑張ってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.31,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,We'll be seeing your game!{NOTE:私たちはついてくるよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.22,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:鮎原君。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:13.65,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Yo.{NOTE:よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, Mitamura-san. Good morning.{NOTE:あら、三田村さん。おはよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:15.70,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Morning.{NOTE:おはよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.30,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun. Do your best tomorrow.{NOTE:鮎原君。明日大いに頑張ってくれたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,I believe in you.{NOTE:おれ勝利を信じてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.56,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yoohoo.{NOTE:ユーフー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,So cool!{NOTE:かっこいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.03,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,You look sweet together.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Good going, Romeo and Juliet!{NOTE:いいぞ、ロミオとジュリエット。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Hahahaha.\N– I'm so jealous.{NOTE:—ハハハハ。\\N—羨ましいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– See you around.\N– Bye.{NOTE:—あの、じゃ。\\N—じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:あ、努君。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It wouldn't hurt for him to encourage me a bit.{NOTE:励ましの声ぐれかけてくれたって言うのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Today is the final practice.{NOTE:さ、今日で練習は最後。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll hold a practice match.{NOTE:XXその試合XX紅白試合をしましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Our opponent is the Soviet Union. Let's do this properly.{NOTE:相手はソ連中だと思って、皆全力出して打っ付かるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:いいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.31,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Yeah!{NOTE:おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:00.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.60,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.12,Default,Ooki,0,0,0,,Receive!{NOTE:つれて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:04.86,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:05.60,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.24,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Good!{NOTE:いいぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.65,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, professor Hongou.{NOTE:あ、本郷先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.58,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Professor Hongou!\N– Professor!{NOTE:—本郷先生！\\N—先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Girls.{NOTE:君たち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I heard you promised to win with the Soviets.{NOTE:ソ連チームに勝つと約束したそうだが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's correct.{NOTE:はい、そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do you think you've got what it takes?{NOTE:本気でそう思ってるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Let me ask again.{NOTE:今一度聞く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can win with the Soviet Union's team?{NOTE:君達は本当にソ連チームに勝てると思っているのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I do.{NOTE:思ってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.90,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– We do.\N– We do.{NOTE:—思ってます。\\N—思ってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:よし、分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.20,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be seeing your game tomorrow.{NOTE:それじゃ、明日の試合は君たちだけでやってみたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Don't forget that spirit.{NOTE:そのファイトを忘れずにな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.74,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:いいな、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,P-Professor, wait.{NOTE:せ-先生、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.37,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Listen, Ayuhara.{NOTE:いいか、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.98,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'm leaving everything to you.{NOTE:全部君に任せるんだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.64,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'll be cheering for you from the seat.{NOTE:僕は応援席で見ている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why is the teacher so cold towards us? Towards me?{NOTE:なぜそこまで先生はバレー部員、あたしに冷たくするんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.78,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's unfair!{NOTE:卑怯者。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.96,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,What is professor Hongou thinking?{NOTE:なにさ、本郷先生なんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.13,Default,Fukuda,0,0,0,,We can win with or without him.{NOTE:コーチしてくれなくちゃって勝てるんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.59,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,On the contrary, we might do better without him.{NOTE:その方があたしたちの(X・株が上がれても)のね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.75,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:—そうよ。\\N—そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.24,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,Let's continue the practice.{NOTE:さ、練習を続けようよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.24,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Yeah!{NOTE:—おう！\\N—おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:よし、やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll bring us a victory even if it kills me.{NOTE:こうなったら、死んでも勝って見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.81,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Hongou-kun.{NOTE:本郷君。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.40,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Sir.{NOTE:校長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:39.69,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,I heard you're no longer coaching the girls. What gives?{NOTE:君。聞くところコーチを休んでるそうだが、どう言うわけかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.76,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It's not only the practice.{NOTE:練習だけではありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I don't intend to coach them in the tomorrow's game too.{NOTE:明日の試合にもコーチを休むつもりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.75,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,As if.{NOTE:まさか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.38,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,You know, this is not funny.{NOTE:君、冗談を言ってる場合じゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.73,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,The opponent is the Soviet Union. Soviet Union!{NOTE:相手はソ連チームですぞ。ソ連。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.34,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I am aware.{NOTE:分かってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.34,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Looks like you're not.{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ、いいえ。分かってはおらん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.63,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,This game isn't just some championship.{NOTE:この試合はだな単なる対抗試合じゃないんだ。}
