Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.56,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,…is because something's troubling you.{NOTE:あなた心の底悩みがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.72,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And you're too proud to admit it.{NOTE:そのXXX心高ぶって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.72,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Of course you can't play well.{NOTE:これでいいXXXできるわけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.80,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor.{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.12,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What should I do?{NOTE:どうしたらいいんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.12,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Please, tell me.{NOTE:お願い、教えて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:20.76,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,H-H-Hongou, you need to do something about this.{NOTE:ほ-ほ-本郷、何とかならんもんかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.48,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:25.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.12,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.13,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Accept!{NOTE:(立って・取って)！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:33.86,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.94,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Higher!{NOTE:XXX！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.64,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, do your best!{NOTE:鮎原さん、頑張って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.49,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Come on!{NOTE:頑張れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.80,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,You can do this!{NOTE:頑張れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I won't say I knew this would happen.{NOTE:こうなるとは分かってるとは言えん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for the girls.{NOTE:これではXXX可愛いそうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,However. However!{NOTE:だが。だが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,This is something they need to learn the hard way.{NOTE:これは一度は味XX知れん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But still.{NOTE:それにしても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara. Good luck!{NOTE:鮎原。頑張るんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hayakawa, you too!{NOTE:早川、しっかりしろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.18,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,One point until Japan needs to admit defeat.{NOTE:後ワンポイントで日本がXXX負け。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.92,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,The match became completely one-sided.{NOTE:勝利は全く絶望的になりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.30,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It's the first time when I can watch Kozue's game.{NOTE:初めてこずえの試合を見に来たんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.84,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Who'd think it'd end up like this.{NOTE:こんな結果になるとは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.46,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,I can't watch it anymore.{NOTE:もう見ていられませんわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.94,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.21,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ、あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:21.74,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,Finally, Japan's representative, Fujimi Academy collapses before the Soviet Union's team.{NOTE:ついにソ連のXXXの前に、日本代表富士見学園チームはXXXました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.94,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,Soviet's junior team is stronger after all.{NOTE:それにしても、強い、ソ連ジュニアチーム。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.72,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We completely lost.{NOTE:とうとう負けてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:36.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We lost without using half of our tricks.{NOTE:XXXプレーやトリックプレーを出すことにできずに負けてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.63,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, my dream is over.{NOTE:あ、これが夢であってくれたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.28,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.71,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,I hate to say it, but…{NOTE:残酷のようだが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.17,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,…but I've been waiting for this day.{NOTE:…僕はこの日は来るの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.92,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,For this situation.{NOTE:…君のその姿を待っていたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.49,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Captain Ayuhara.{NOTE:キャプテン鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:20:59.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,The power your team has shown us in the All-Japan tournament…{NOTE:あなたたちこの前の全国大会で見せてくれた実力…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.18,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,…wasn't there today.{NOTE:十分発揮しなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Yours especially.{NOTE:特にあなたそうでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:26.06,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara, let's meet again.{NOTE:鮎原。又きっときっと会いましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.58,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Good bye.{NOTE:それでさようなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.02,Default (ru),Shellenina,0,0,0,,До свидания.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina wants to play again in the future, but…{NOTE:シェレーニナは「又会おう」と言ってくれたけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:だけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,…no matter how you look at it, it's over.{NOTE:これは何もかもお終いだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:06.78,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,– You said we'll win.\N– You call yourself captain?{NOTE:—何やってんだよ？大きいなXXX。\\N—XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:10.10,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,You were so full of yourself.{NOTE:XXXあんなXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I was thinking about this all night long without sleep.{NOTE:昨夜一晩中寝ないで考えたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor, I've decided.{NOTE:先生、あたし決心しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:18.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Please disband the volleyball club.{NOTE:バレー部を解散してください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.48,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Say what?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.{NOTE:もうだめです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:24.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Without the new gym, our club cannot go on.{NOTE:バレー部専用体育館でころか、バレーさえこれ以上続けられません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:26.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Everything is over.{NOTE:何もかも終わりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:30.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Y-You still don't get it, do you?{NOTE:き-きみは未だ分からんのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:36.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,If that's all you're thinking, be\hmy guest and quit volleyball.{NOTE:そんな考えしかできんのなら、望みどおりバレーなんか止めてしまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But the club isn't for you only.{NOTE:だが君一人のためにバレー部はあるんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:42.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,If you quit, do it by yourself.{NOTE:止めるなら、君一人で止めろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Understood?{NOTE:いいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:そうします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Cool down for a bit and think why you were playing volleyball thus far.{NOTE:少し頭を冷やして、何のためにバレーをやるのかよく考えてみろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Do not come back until you figure it out.{NOTE:それが分かるまで二度とバレー部に戻ってくるなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:02.54,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.60,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,When will you understand?{NOTE:何時俺は分かってくれるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:05.40,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,When?{NOTE:何時？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:06.18,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,When?!{NOTE:何時？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,This felt refreshing.{NOTE:これでさっぱりしたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I assumed responsibility.{NOTE:あたしはこれで責任を取ったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Who are you kidding?{NOTE:それで責任を取ったつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.71,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You just ran away.{NOTE:あなたはただ逃げたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:18.70,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's not it!{NOTE:違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I assumed my responsibility as the captain.{NOTE:キャプテンとして責任を取ったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:22.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,With this, I bid my farewell to volleyball.{NOTE:これでバレーとのいっさいお別れ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:24.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:26.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can quit volleyball?{NOTE:本気でバレーが止められると思ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:29.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can quit.{NOTE:止められるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.94,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"What are you playing volleyball for?"{NOTE:何のためにバレーをやるのかですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter anymore.{NOTE:そんなこともう関係ないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:35.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Who cares.{NOTE:知るもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:56.52,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Soviet Team's coach unexpectedly approaches Kozue…{NOTE:XXXにもソ連チームのコーチはこずえを訪れ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:00.42,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,…and sends her to the pine grove, where Shellenina is waiting.{NOTE:…シェレーニナは待っていると言う千本松原へこずえを連れ出した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:02.96,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Shellenina speaks harshly to Kozue.{NOTE:シェレーニナは厳しくこずえに迫った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:05.57,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,"I can't forgive you the yesterday's match."{NOTE:機能の試合ぶりを許せないと言うのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.11,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,"What is volleyball about?"{NOTE:バレーボールはどんなものか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.79,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,—she proclaims and declares she wants to show their last game in Japan.{NOTE:日本での最後の試合を見せたいと言う…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:13.70,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,The opponent is a high school boys' team.{NOTE:…その試合とはなんと、高校男子チームXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:16.56,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Shellenina shows Kozue the match.{NOTE:さて、試合はシェレーニナはこずえに見せおとした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:19.29,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,It unfolds to be a terrifying game.{NOTE:恐るべきプレーに向かって進んでいった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:23.04,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
